<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_90_r1l1"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Hannſ<ex>en</ex></expan> von Stawff ʒu Ernfels </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_90_r1l2"><expan>pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒum Beheimſtein </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_90_r1l3"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan> als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>s</expan> knechts <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> der bey </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_90_r1l4">vns ʒu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> geſtochen ıſt <expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan> etc Das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_90_r1l5">Vnd laſſen eẅr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>wiſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / alſbald wır des erJnnert <expan>wurde<ex>n</ex></expan> / daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_90_r1l6">wır nach den dıe daran ſchuldıg <expan>ſull<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſein . <expan>ernſtl<ex>ich</ex></expan> geſtellt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_90_r1l7">vnd Jſt auch der einer der vns daran <expan>v<ex>er</ex>leẅmunt</expan> wart . bey vns <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_90_r1l8">auf <expan>geſt<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu fenknuſſ bracht / vvır <expan>künne<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> an Jm niht fınden </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_90_r1l9">daʒ er ſchuldıg daran ſey / Denn vns ıſt einer vermeltt <expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan> . der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_90_r1l10">es getan ſol <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . der ıſt auch gewychen / vnd möchten wır hin </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_90_r1l11">für darcʒu ıht getun . daʒ dıe ſache gepüſſet wurd . das <expan>wölt<ex>en</ex></expan> wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_90_r1l12"><expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> tun vvan wır ſölıch ſache bey vns niht <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ſehen . Vnd wo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_90_line_1576676661822_4465">wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> etc . <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ııȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>om<ex>n</ex>ȷ</expan> <expan>ſ<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>o<ex>rum</ex></expan> </ab>
